{"tid":665456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方展開打擊公共車輛司機違規行為行動，於元朗區內拘捕3名小巴司機，並扣留5部小巴。","createTime":"2018-05-15T03:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T06:07:31.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"137c9c29186d970913f35509e064d1f304c8d597","tid":665456,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:29:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3小巴司機涉非法加裝座位被捕 警票控15乘客無佩戴安全帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1215735/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1215735%2F&d=19Onf4KoFeeu3uVua%2B1FOmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=4713d61f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1215735%2F&h=e47aaea0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1215735/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180514/_2018051419084267701.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180514%2F_2018051419084267701.jpeg&h=97c484b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有司機使用過期滅火筒、非法加裝座位位及 遮擋司機證，3項違規。</span></div>"},{"pid":"08a9fd45189e4e611fc3eadd068b49b81458e181","tid":665456,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:31:19.000Z","msg":"新界北總區交通部特遣隊吳慶張督察表示，於5月6日、11日及14日的清晨時份，在元朗區內分別截停3部小巴，並拘捕3名司機，分別為61歲姓黃、59歲姓劉及66歲姓李司機。他們涉嫌危險駕駛、切雙白線、非法加裝座位、車上滅火筒過期、司機位安全帶失效等。其中姓劉小巴司機為通緝人士。兩名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於6月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180514/_2018051419043112234.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180514%2F_2018051419043112234.jpeg&h=e2a15ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">小巴的車尾亦放有座位。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n另外，5輛小巴涉嫌違反《道路交通（車輛構造及保養）規例》，被扣查作進一步檢驗，其中一部小巴涉嫌於逃生門前加裝座位，須扣留檢查。警方亦向17名司機發出定額罰款通知書，當中包括在駕駛時以手持方式使用流動電話、沒有遵從交通燈號及連續橫過雙白線，及票控15名未有佩戴安全帶的小巴乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180514/_2018051419043297355.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180514%2F_2018051419043297355.jpeg&h=878b649b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有小巴司機在車上使用過期滅火筒。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n警方表示，會繼續採取執法行動，打擊危害道路使用者安全及相關的不法活動，並呼籲市民及公共服務車輛司機如有資料提供，可與警方聯絡。"},{"pid":"339b512c1bb5f610e90338ec5c8aa64acd369307","tid":665456,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"果日俾人撚完而家發惡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b5bb0abc8e1974543f8a320b132b904405950b","tid":665456,"uid":51532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"乘客比人捉係邊個比罰款？"},{"pid":"dd14890fb69edbf70fcf930c8cdd2f6625190b5c","tid":665456,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:40:12.000Z","msg":"佔中影響"},{"pid":"ef2b6e3c458d73d3158d18ff9ab4485c4887f9a9","tid":665456,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:41:38.000Z","msg":"未交保護費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港有邊架紅van冇加位超載？有時夜晚連企位都有，而家先黎捉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023224e50de4175cb5c547cc631147e3a4ad1cd2","tid":665456,"uid":5587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T03:44